title: New York Governor Andrew Cuomo Backs American Jobs Act | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
September 09, 2011

 



New York Governor Andrew Cuomo Backs American Jobs Act





	GOVERNOR CUOMO STATEMENT ON PRESIDENT OBAMA'S JOBS ADDRESS

	"Tonight, President Obama laid out a real plan to jumpstart the economy and put Americans back to work. The President realizes that it is essential that creating jobs be the top priority at all levels of government. As the President said, politics cannot come before the urgent need to put Americans back to work. This is a plan that can and should be supported by officials of all political stripes and we need to see the Congress move this nation forward."Â
